From Nancy Patricia O'Connor Subject Re THE POPE IS JEWISH In article Stilgar writes Last night while watching the rebroadcast of Jerry Springer a talk show I heard this Jewel of a thought from a year old The focus of this show was on these kids and their hatred for the Jewish religion and some stuff deleted Interesting and scary no They went on to say how the Jews had killed their god and how in the end of time that all the races would go to their homelands of course they would remain in America which is New Jeruselem as it says in Gen what another kid said but the rest of the races would go home and then the great battle or plague or whatever says would happen and the jews would be The most interesting thing about this was that my roomate is Catholic and had the KJV of the Bible on his He immediatly opened it up and began to search for the quoted passages Gen Rev and John to look for himself and couldn't find what they said they I don't know I saw this show a while back and when I heard these kids quote the Bible to justify their racist claims I looked up that quote about Jesus hating Jews since Jesus himself was a Jew my curiousity had been piqued by such a claim The jist of the passage and I am sorry but I can't recall which passage it was exactly was that Jesus was condemning the Pharisees for being Of course the Pharisees were Jewish too but it wasn't Jews as a whole that Jesus was condemning just the powers that Nancy O'Connor Psychology undergrad The opinions I express Simon Fraser University are my Burnaby CANADA